name: Acrisure - Voice Agent with Email & Attachments (Gmail)

parameters.content:
## Acrisure Voice Agent - Complete

### Features:
1. Licensed/Unlicensed Classification
2. Google Gemini AI
3. Email with Attachments (Gmail)
4. Google Drive File Retrieval

### Webhook Input:
```json
{
  "question": "User question",
  "email": "customer@email.com",
  "sendEmail": true,
  "attachFiles": true
}
```

### Setup:
1. Configure Google Sheets credentials
2. Configure Google Gemini API
3. Configure Gmail OAuth2
4. Configure Google Drive OAuth2
5. Update folder ID for quote files
